{"ts": "2026-06-09T16:33:10.629778+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:Mh9R2O | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 14cdb62b2e100f4ebf75f88cf5c58669437208e3)", "id": "lc_ff26d22e-a818-42aa-835c-e65faadf9a93"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:Mh9R2O | # vue3-vite-starter-template\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | A single page app [Vite](https://vitejs.dev) starter template, created to easily bootstrap Vue.js 3 apps.\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | **Features**\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Vitest for unit testing\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Pinia for state management\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Vue Router 4 for client-side routing\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Bootstrap 5.3 for layout and styling\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - SCSS variables inside Vue components\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Purgecss for eliminating unused CSS\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Basic multiple layouts feature\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - ESLint config based on `eslint:recommended` with sensible defaults :relaxed:\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - [Prettier](https://prettier.io/) for code formatting\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | - Automated release workflow with [semantic-release](https://github.com/semantic-release/semantic-release)\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ## Project setup\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | pnpm install\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ### Compiles and hot-reloads for development\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | pnpm run dev\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ### Compiles and minifies for production\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | pnpm run build\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ## Run your unit tests\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | pnpm run test:unit\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ### Lints files\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | pnpm run lint\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ### Lints and fixes files\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | npm run lint-fix\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ```\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | ### Customize configuration\n| MCP:Mh9R2O | \n| MCP:Mh9R2O | See [Configuration Reference](https://vitejs.dev/guide/).", "id": "lc_85b30868-e2a2-4321-ab70-c18fa85ff416"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "b7a99d53-1293-4c1a-bda1-036a938e3f50", "tool_call_id": "call_051624a3a6ed4976bc43d78a", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
