{"ts": "2026-06-09T16:33:25.266793+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are the **setup and day-to-day development commands** for this Vue 3 + Vite project:\n\n---\n\n### Prerequisites\n- **Node.js**: v24 (specified in `.nvmrc`)\n- **Package Manager**: pnpm 10.20.0 (enforced via `preinstall` script)\n\n---\n\n### Commands\n\n| Action | Command |\n|---|---|\n| **Install dependencies** | `pnpm install` |\n| **Dev server** (hot-reload) | `pnpm run dev` |\n| **Build** (production) | `pnpm run build` |\n| **Preview production build** | `pnpm run preview` |\n| **Build + preview** | `pnpm run build-preview` |\n| **Unit tests** | `pnpm run test:unit` |\n| **Unit tests with coverage** | `pnpm run test:unit-coverage` |\n| **Lint** | `pnpm run lint` |\n| **Lint & auto-fix** | `pnpm run lint-fix` |\n\n---\n\n### Additional Notes\n- **Linting** uses ESLint targeting `*.{vue,ts,js}` files.\n- **Formatting** is handled by Prettier (config in `prettier.config.js`).\n- **Commit linting** is enforced via Husky git hooks + commitlint (conventional commits).\n- **Lint-staged** runs automatically on staged files before commits (config in `lint-staged.config.js`).\n- **Testing** uses Vitest with `@vue/test-utils` and jsdom.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 344, "prompt_tokens": 9944, "total_tokens": 10288, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 14, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 9728}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "ce4982cddfc24070ae770610102681b7", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ead3b-2253-7d72-b02f-640a8640cbab-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9944, "output_tokens":